metadata.name: BnB Issue 1 Cover: What Lurks Amoung the Mangroves
metadata.description: PREMIERE ISSUE! Beasts and Babes debut cover. A magazine for those who like sexy beasts and dangerous beauties. Don't miss the wild tales and spicy art. With our in house survivalist expert, Sgt. Tiger Johnson, giving proven advice based on his own real life experience. You don't want to lose track of this publication.
